description:
Okinii is inspired by Azuki, yet trying to establish an brand new culture and story on BRC20 Okinii, a term rooted in Japanese culture, stands for the value of respect, dignity, and elegance, encapsulating the ethos behind our unique initiative.

We invite you to join us on this exhilarating journey and witness the dawning of a new era in digital art, powered by the revolution of Bitcoin NFTs. Welcome to the world of Okinii, where creativity meets innovation, and art transcends the digital frontier.
name: Okinii
